* prototypes for the functions should be in the text manipulation.h file.
* Your code must be written in the file text manipulation.c.
* Do not add a main function to the text manipulation.c file
* One source of bugs is forgetting to add a null character to a string
* Do not use dynamic memory allocation

* gcc public01.c text manipulation.c
* gcc -ansi -Wall -g -O0 -Wwrite-strings -Wshadow -pedantic-errors -fstack-protector-all 

